Ok well ive been in the middle of a big week so im gonna tell you about everything thats happened since friday cuz i forgot to update.

Friday: Friday started off normal. i just sat around on the computer cuz there was nothing to do and thats all i could do. then i went to the drive-in to see spiderman 2 and it was wicked good. i went with my family and cathy and alex and when we saw sam and lauren and i hung out with them and then i saw courtney so it was cool. Spiderman was wicked good and it was fun to randomly WaLk ArOuNd the screen with sam and lauren adn then cathy and alex. we must go again soon!

Saturday: I went to my aunt and uncles 4th Of July party. even tho it was the third. it was a pool party so we hung out in the pool and ate food. then we had a baseball game and i wasnt caring at all if i won or lost and i unintentionally won the game for my team with my homer and then my RBI. then it was too late to go see the fireworks so i watched em from my house and it was just as good i guess.

Sunday: Well it was the 4th Of July so it was a good day. the soccer tournament i talked about earlier had its final and portugal made it so we had to have a big PARTY. in the end portugal lost so there were a lot of mad portugeese ppl in my house.but it was still all good.

Monday: well on monday there really was nothing to do. it rained so basically i just talked on the phone and watched DVDs and stuff. that was pretty much my whole day. i only woke up at like 1 so not much of a day.

Tuesday (today): i had to go to the library to get the stupid summer reading books and i went with julie so it was fun. we went in and this librarian like stalked us down to get us to sign up for their summer reading junk but as soon as we found our books we ran out just in time! and  then i came home and had delicious tacos that were so good i must have them again! well mr collins e-mailed me and said that its true that he was laid off but he expects to get rehired by the end of the summer so thats good news! well thats pretty much everything that happened. well now! COMMENTok tty all later...
